'''Peepee''' is a slang term used to denote either the male or female sexual organ, or the waste product, urine. Typically, the term "peepee" is a juvenile usage, although it may be used by adults who are speaking to children and who believe that the more clinical terms "penis" or "vagina" should be reserved for later stages of life, or who themselves may, as adults, remain uncomfortable with such usage. The dual (organ/waste product) meaning of the term can result in interesting phrases, such as "don't get peepee on your peepee" or one's "peepee makes peepee", a seemingly perpetual peepee motion machine.